txt.en: 'That is the horn. On the third sounding, we charge.'
'Fear not, brothers. Men and Elves allied - we are unstoppable!'
'Go now! Fly! I will lead you if I must. I will - ugh! Oh....'
'Months we have battled and now the time is come.'
'Five and fifty Orcs I've slain this day.'
'Let me kill or be killed, for all of war is death.'
'Whence came that arrow? It burns... burns in my side.'
'I will lie here and here will be my grave. Never go home to Arnor. Never see my kin.'
'The pain. The roar of battle. All dims... all fades....'
